solution:
Label points $O,A,B,C,D,E$ as follows.

[asy]
draw((0,0) -- (3,0) -- (3,3) -- (0,3)--cycle) ; draw((3,0)-- (12,0) -- (12,9) -- (3, 9)--cycle);

label ( "3", (0,1.5), W); label ( "3", (1.5 ,0), S); label ( "9", (3+9/2 ,0), S);label ( "9", (12 ,9/2), E);
